geometric figures

00:18:14.080 --> 00:18:17.540 align:middle line:84%
are spread over its
entire expansion.

00:18:17.540 --> 00:18:20.450 align:middle line:84%
Only from above is it
possible to realize

00:18:20.450 --> 00:18:24.820 align:middle line:84%
the true essence of the
shapes traced on the ground.

00:18:24.820 --> 00:18:28.030 align:middle line:84%
The Nazca Plain is one
of the planet's driest

00:18:28.030 --> 00:18:31.060 align:middle line:90%
and most inhospitable.

00:18:31.060 --> 00:18:35.650 align:middle line:84%
In fact, rainfall only amounts
to 1 cubic centimeter per year,

00:18:35.650 --> 00:18:37.930 align:middle line:84%
more or less a quarter
of an hour of rain

00:18:37.930 --> 00:18:39.280 align:middle line:90%
over a 12 month span.

00:18:39.280 --> 00:18:41.800 align:middle line:90%


00:18:41.800 --> 00:18:45.760 align:middle line:84%
A real hellish,
barren, and stony land,

00:18:45.760 --> 00:18:48.220 align:middle line:84%
but at the same
time, the ideal place

00:18:48.220 --> 00:18:51.190 align:middle line:84%
to trace images which
can remain unchanged

00:18:51.190 --> 00:18:53.442 align:middle line:90%
throughout the centuries.

00:18:53.442 --> 00:18:56.330 align:middle line:90%
>> [SPEAKING SPANISH]

00:18:56.330 --> 00:18:58.350 align:middle line:90%
