with an accuracy which

00:20:47.660 --> 00:20:49.970 align:middle line:84%
has baffled researchers
who have examined them.

00:20:49.970 --> 00:20:53.620 align:middle line:90%


00:20:53.620 --> 00:20:55.360 align:middle line:84%
The zoomorphic
drawings have been

00:20:55.360 --> 00:20:58.160 align:middle line:84%
