excavation equipment

00:36:33.730 --> 00:36:38.440 align:middle line:84%
would be required with
long working days.

00:36:38.440 --> 00:36:42.015 align:middle line:84%
But the tunnels are not
the only Marcahuasi enigma.

00:36:42.015 --> 00:36:45.200 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:36:45.200 --> 00:36:48.210 align:middle line:84%
The plateau is also
the showcase of dozens

00:36:48.210 --> 00:36:51.808 align:middle line:84%
of mysterious drawings found
and catalogued buy Ruzo.

00:36:51.808 --> 00:36:55.154 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:36:55.154 --> 00:36:58.510 align:middle line:90%


