The archaeologist claimed that
the technique used by the Masma

00:37:01.640 --> 00:37:04.270 align:middle line:84%
to carve the Marcahuasi
rocks differs

00:37:04.270 --> 00:37:07.420 align:middle line:90%
from any known to mankind.

00:37:07.420 --> 00:37:11.110 align:middle line:84%
He defined it organic
sculpture and believed

00:37:11.110 --> 00:37:13.900 align:middle line:84%
it derived from extremely
advanced knowledge

00:37:13.900 --> 00:37:17.050 align:middle line:84%
from a different way of viewing
reality and representing

00:37:17.050 --> 00:37:22.820 align:middle line:84%
shapes, a world where magical
power and the earth and sky

00:37:22.820 --> 00:37:25.520 align:middle line:84%
bond were of
fundamental importance.

00:37:25.520 --> 00:37:28.502 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

