In my personal opinion,
it seems obvious

00:37:53.000 --> 00:37:55.190 align:middle line:84%
that these were extremely
well-prepared people

00:37:55.190 --> 00:37:59.000 align:middle line:84%
with another type of mentality,
a very special civilization

00:37:59.000 --> 00:38:01.490 align:middle line:90%
with great knowledge.

